sources.title: Don't Marry Your Daughter (1934) by Willy Rozier | Family Ties Twist and Cross the Love Lines
sources.description:
Baroness schemes to set up her friend Alerme with Jewett, a wealthy asparagus mogul. But when Jewett falls for Alerme’s daughter Jeannine, the baroness shifts gears to seal the deal for the younger match.

Original title: N'épouse pas ta fille (Don't Marry Your Daughter)

Director: Willy Rozier
Writers: Pierre Chaume, Willy Rozier
Stars: Fernande Albany, Louis Blanche, Balder, Marguerite Templey
Genres:  French cinema, Comedy
Release date: April 20, 1934 (France)
